author: Catherine Pulsifer
message: Rather than wishing for change, you first must be prepared to change.
title: Thought of the day

author: Buddha
message: I do not believe in a fate that falls on men however they act; but I do believe in a fate that falls on them unless they act.
title: Thought of the day

author: Holmes
message: Fame usually comes to those who are thinking about something else.
title: Thought of the day

author: Napoleon Hill
message: First comes thought; then organization of that thought, into ideas and plans; then transformation of those plans into reality. The beginning, as you will observe, is in your imagination.
title: Thought of the day
